29 to conversion charter schools pursuant to Act 2024-428
30 to be used as needed by the conversion charter schools.
31 This bill would also amend Act 2025-270, the
32 Education Appropriation Act for the fiscal year ending
33 September 30, 2026, to clarify the intent of an
34 appropriation to the Department of Public Health.
