104 shall be distributed according to the fleet renewal guidelines
105 to be used for the purchase of school buses or the retirement
106 of school bus debt. For any school system that is currently up
107 to date in purchasing regular route buses, application may be
108 made to the State Superintendent of Education to flex these
109 funds for other educational purposes.
